"signal_description": "The SIGNAL query is calculating a percentage from the 'defaultview-57' table. It first sums up the count of 'PR Id' where 'Event Created By User Type' is either 'System' or 'Service' and the 'event_name' contains 'PR'. This sum is then divided by the total count of 'PR Id' where 'event_name' contains 'PR'. The result of this division is then multiplied by 100 to get the percentage. The final result will give the percentage of 'PR Id' that were created by either 'System' or 'Service' and have 'PR' in their 'event_name' out of all 'PR Id' that have 'PR' in their 'event_name'."
}
